title: Video to Picture : image from video ( APK Android )
description:
Video to Picture (image from video) allows easy creation image from a video.

-- Features --

- 50 different filters for images from a video.
- Batch processing images from a video (from the segment A to B).
- Easily convert video to picture, just set the desired frame.
- You can choose a different resolution for new image from a video.
- Save image from video as jpg or png format.
- Manage your video and image files.
- With Video to Picture you can also view your video and picture.



[b]Required Android O/S : 4.0+[/b]




Smalled APK size from Google Play ( 6M instead of 16M ) :
         
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.livecodedev.video_to_jpg
